dbdfda62634ac2f7c6e655bf","tid":2288184,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e39d7ade0f3bd080eeed8f3cdbd915716baf2f","tid":2288184,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"問題在於2個月時間點拆, 係無去狗屋報失,定點冇資料<br />\n新聞又只係提官根據打扮黎屈入佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉官指案發時未有肺炎，被告的衣著打扮是刻意遮蓋容貌以免被認出，而黑色噴油存放在背包的外側袋，被告出現的位置只距離車站30米外，且裝束與破壞者相似。雖然法庭未能確定破壞者必然是被告，但從其掩飾的方式看來，顯然是掩耳盜鈴，可合理推論他有意圖摧毀財產，裁定罪成。"},{"pid":"20a8422b87a2dcc0222bdb9df4bbb5110fd22bff","tid":2288184,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140eb69c30490f14412697d5c79bd546e667b427","tid":2288184,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5e39d7ade0f3bd080eeed8f3cdbd915716baf2f","tid":2288184,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"問題在於2個月時間點拆, 係無去狗屋報失,定點冇資料<br />\n新聞又只係提官根據打扮黎屈入佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉官指案發時未有肺炎，被告的衣著打扮是刻意遮蓋容貌以免被認出，而黑色噴油存放在背包的外側袋，被告出現的位置只距離車站30米外，且裝束與破壞者相似。雖然法庭未能確定破壞者必然是被告，但從其掩飾的方式看來，顯然是掩耳盜鈴，可合理推論他有意圖摧毀財產，裁定罪成。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d57075da231b3295ed4d969fa8